{"tid":45212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重貼走殘體]世界大黑店 igshop@Keepersneaker","createTime":"2016-12-18T20:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T17:43:56.000Z","uid":67588,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6699de78c5970f72fa438ad745f4270877b4d3","tid":45212,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:55:05.000Z","msg":"即使幾多人follow既ig shop <br />\n都係會呃人<br />\n<br />\n小弟代朋友開po 希望取回公道<br />\n已經準備透過小額錢債索<br />\n<br />\n事件起因: <br />\n事主係Keepsneaker網店訂購左貨<br />\n<br />\nUltra Boost 3.0 Triple White<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/044859_69f6f0bde838e537005ac0c6672dd555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F044859_69f6f0bde838e537005ac0c6672dd555.jpg&h=7736f242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n價錢:1599hkd<br />\n<br />\n當時事主透過ATM機過數<br />\n手快冇拎到入數紙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/044926_28467b333fa0dbb38c6772ff78a015d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F044926_28467b333fa0dbb38c6772ff78a015d8.jpg&h=71b5d5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但透過銀行紀錄 已經同店主確認左入數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入數之後 店主表示貨品價錢有變動<br />\n詢問事主重要唔要對鞋<br />\n如果唔要 店主會退返錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aj4cwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aj4cwQ.jpg&h=b887e6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主想問下ultra boost uncaged價錢<br />\n但最後事主係第日決定退錢<br />\n而店主亦以okay回覆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/044954_e41474b0de6519f441182ea81a4b79e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F044954_e41474b0de6519f441182ea81a4b79e6.jpg&h=34a7370b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事後幾日 事主再查詢退款安排之際<br />\n店主亦沒有作出仼何回應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主嘗試打電話<br />\n但個號碼只係有whatsapp<br />\n並唔能夠打通<br />\n<br />\n事主之後係Keepsneaker ig貼文留言<br />\n但遭到店主删去留言並且即是封鎖用戶<br />\n<br />\n事主另外幾位幫手既朋友亦被封鎖抹去留言<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上係店舖資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/045012_ca07a3da164c364547a4c0cf089efc1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F045012_ca07a3da164c364547a4c0cf089efc1e.jpg&h=dba1c11a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIG: Keepersneaker<br />\n電話(只有whatsapp): 9558 - 5373<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZ06MqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZ06MqJ.jpg&h=76e07d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀行戶口<br />\n滙豐銀行 124 411 836 838<br />\n恆生銀行 789 287 638 883<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主一定要揭露出呢間ig shop的醜惡<br />\n<br />\n口口聲話已經開業4年 信譽保證<br />\n但呢位店主以為拖得就拖 毫無退款意慾<br />\n<br />\n請各位認住呢一間擁有超過一萬followers既網店<br />\n<br />\n事主正考慮尋求法律意見<br />\n<br />\n為了比壓力呢位店主<br />\n懇求各位幫個忙<br />\n係呢間無良ig shop既貼文上<br />\n留低一句<br />\n<br />\n&quot;我屌你老母 你幾時還錢&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed59e7da28dab0071e30ceac6f756fda1d9e62ef","tid":45212,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T21:05:00.000Z","msg":"店主偷偷留下負皮<br />\n<br />\n重偷偷改埋名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6NMFO2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6NMFO2.jpg&h=0e781299&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52f9d5cb46b825b4bb9540e5fd066ca628570761","tid":45212,"uid":30433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T21:06:19.000Z","msg":"真心唔敢上網買鞋<br />\n都唔知係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0f0217fc112948dbb8dcefe2fc89905f347c8d","tid":45212,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi